I don’t normally apply but here we go.

Date of Birth: I am 19.

What I have to offer? Well simple:

  1. I have a 8gb linux dedi that I can run the server off of (I know how to run a rs off of CentOS)
  2. I am pretty decent at PHP, I can configure the server so it has a full online panel, so players can edit, register and alter their account.
  3. I am also great at java, if you want to see what I can do or I might even release some examples, if you wish!
    I can keep going, I already have a vbulletin license, hosting (seperate from the dedi) ect…
  4. I am a marketing wiz, hell I know how SEO works in and out.

Finally previous work? I did PHP work a while back for Yanille.com, its still running and the owner makes bank! on a shitty source.

What I can offer basically.
A) A Forum / Website that is full intergraded with the server
B) A soild dedi to run the server off of and it will be 24/7
C) I already wrote a decent Quest Manager and a decent PI-based Dungoun system (NOT THE SKILL BUT MORE LIKE SURVIVAL FROM COD) hmm yeah, i will leave it at that.
If you need to contact me, shoot me an email.
